
## Preparation for Your New Vinterkold  


Efficiently draining your Vinterkold.  


## Normal Drainage.  


To drain water, pull out the drainage valve and rotate the cap counterclockwise.  

![](images/0.jpg)
  


Water will begin to drain. Pushing the valve inwards increases the water flow, while pulling it out reduces the water flow.  

![](images/1.jpg)
  


To stop the drainage, rotate the cap clockwise and push the valve inwards.  

![](images/2.jpg)
